‚ùå `text-intents-ux-textSubtle-textColor` ‚Üí ‚úÖ `text-intents-ux-feedbackHighContrastPassive-feedbackColor`
‚ùå `text-intents-ux-text-textColor` ‚Üí ‚úÖ `text-intents-ux-box-foregroundColor`
